        {
            "title": "44歲女星痛毆中風父  父突陳屍家中失救無援  爆喊自責後悔莫及",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"44歲女星痛毆中風父  父突陳屍家中失救無援  爆喊自責後悔莫及\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6451adce55e000a0c70ca107c3d32046/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040914555468994.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">44歲女星痛毆中風父  父突陳屍家中失救無援  爆喊自責後悔莫及</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>現年44歲的台灣女星、模特兒林可彤，近日於節目《女王大人》中憶起當年過世的父親，過程曲折非常傷感。當年25歲的她父親突然中風，林可彤獨自擔起家中經濟重擔，兩人又因相處不睦，常激烈爭吵甚至大打出手，林可彤甚至會趕走父親不讓他歸家。沒想到某年中秋節她因怕塞車，未回家看父親，因此錯過父親最後一面，讓她深感遺憾。\n\n</p><h2>林可彤曾被爸爸施暴</h2>\n<p>林可彤近日到節目《女王大人》分享此生最刻骨銘心的生離死別，提及自己當時才25歲，父親在經商失敗後性格大變，曾經對她施暴。某天她回家時突發覺父親精神狀況很奇怪，送進急診時被診斷為中風，沒想到回家後不到半年就離開，讓她相當難過，淚灑攝影棚。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3444912/%E5%8A%89%E5%B0%8F%E6%85%A7%E5%BC%B7%E5%BF%8D%E6%B7%9A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9B%A3%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%A5%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8B%E7%94%9F%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E9%A1%98%E6%83%B3%E7%9D%87%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82\">劉小慧強忍淚水難接受李國祥已離開 稱好友生前有心願：想睇到兩個小朋友快樂</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185345/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤和丈夫有個美滿的家庭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e61dfec9ca1156d738892e4b995c7b9/2025-04/1_1_29.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤和丈夫有個美滿的家庭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185346/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤很愛錫兒子。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aeb6364ac56296d5a6025d097fad84f5/2025-04/2_2_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤很愛錫兒子。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185347/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤很愛錫兒子。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8036f4a203be84425dc9de14da634ef/2025-04/3_3_8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤很愛錫兒子。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185348/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤近日於節目中大爆當日父親去世經過。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/daf24517467d3aa3e32beeb3970c62be/2025-04/4_3_4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤近日於節目中大爆當日父親去世經過。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185349/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤因為怕塞車，沒有回家看望父親。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7ab65ce5b3bfbe2b17f10ec65e2515e/2025-04/5_4_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤因為怕塞車，沒有回家看望父親。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185350/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤估不到因此錯過見父親最後一面。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c39148856aab172ae1129d3a1848de12/2025-04/6_2_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤估不到因此錯過見父親最後一面。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185351/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤父親於家中失救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dab0ca03df9fd98734be055fb880de68/2025-04/7_2_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤父親於家中失救。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185352/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤父親在自己的家過世。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c4eaa6f612582714ea206096aecc0a5/2025-04/8_3_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤父親在自己的家過世。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185353/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤透露曾和父親大打出手。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e96218150c8659d77b3021739b88c45/2025-04/9_18.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤透露曾和父親大打出手。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185354/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林可彤指父親過世後，十年也走不出來。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17c8f1d719e1df39d92b565a6415c538/2025-04/10_17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林可彤指父親過世後，十年也走不出來。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>林可彤未能見上爸爸最後一面</h2>\n<p>林可彤透露，當時適逢中秋節，但因為她很怕塞車，所以打電話告訴父親節日過後再回去看他，但沒想到父親突然在家中過世，她也連最後一面也沒見上，讓她相當自責，覺得應該要在節日時就回家，也很難過自己忙着賺錢，卻沒有趁父親還在時多陪伴他，並多着緊他身體早點帶他看醫生。\n\n</p><h2>林可彤和爸爸曾大打出手</h2>\n<p>林可彤提到，在父親過世前，自己與他還是經常爭吵，甚至在雙方互打後，叫父親離開她家，幾天後父親又會回來，直到父親過世後，她長達10年都走不出來，經常作惡夢，夢到父親過得不好，直到10年後，才夢到父親跟她告別，才總算釋懷。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3443233/%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%8B%E6%A6%AE%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%9622%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%A8%E6%96%87%E8%8F%AF%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%96%E7%8F%BE%E8%8A%B1%E6%B5%B7-%E6%AD%8C%E8%BF%B7%E6%8E%92%E9%95%B7%E9%BE%8D%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%A0%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%AF%A8%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E5%93%A5%E8%BF%B7\">張國榮逝世22周年丨文華東方酒店外現花海 歌迷排長龍悼念 少女因《九龍城寨之圍城》成為「哥迷」</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
